nter-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/jack-antonoff-sabrina-carpenter-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/jack-antonoff-sabrina-carpenter-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/jack-antonoff-sabrina-carpenter-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>本周末<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/sabrina-carpenter">，萨布丽娜·卡彭特 (Sabrina Carpenter)</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/jack-antonoff">杰克·安东诺夫 (Jack Antonoff)</a>在格莱美博物馆联手演奏了一首新歌《Slim Pickins》。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-features/espresso-sabrina-carpenter-spotify-streaming-3757741"><b>为什么 Sabrina Carpenter 的“Espresso”会接管 Spotify 算法？</b></a></strong></li></ul><p> 8 月 2 日，卡彭特与她的合作者安东诺夫一起出现在洛杉矶格莱美博物馆的克莱夫·戴维斯剧院，进行了主持的讨论和表演。</p><p>她演奏了她即将发行的专辑《 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/heres-the-tracklist-for-sabrina-carpenters-new-album-short-n-sweet-3773425">Short n&#39; Sweet</a> 》中未发行的歌曲，令歌迷们感到惊讶。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="Sabrina Carpenter 和 Jack Antonoff 的《Slim Pickings》（现场）" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/eF44-ERtkus?start=1&enablejsapi=1#038;feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>当晚的粉丝镜头显示，这位“羽毛”歌手告诉观众：“这首歌很可爱，我就是喜欢，今天想为你们唱这首歌。我超级随意，所以，它被称为“Slim Pickins”，我希望你喜欢它。”</p><p>卡彭特还在安东诺夫的支持下表演了“Please Please Please”和“Espresso”， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/sabrina-carpenter-announces-new-album-short-n-sweet-3762089">她于六月宣布她的第六张录音室专辑将于本月晚些时候发行</a>，随后将进行<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/sabrina-carpenter-announces-2024-north-american-the-short-n-sweet-tour-3767338">“Short n&#39; Sweet”巡演</a>。查找下面的日期并<a href="https://ticketmaster.evyy.net/c/2862475/264167/4272?sharedid=NME&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.